<p>refer:<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73559113/uninitialized-class-variable-schemes-in-uri">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73559113/uninitialized-class-variable-schemes-in-uri</a></p>

<p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/ask/sof/107255281/answer/116581440">https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/ask/sof/107255281/answer/116581440</a></p>

<p>根据提示，我增加了gem,</p>

<p><code>gem &#39;globalid&#39;</code></p>

<p>但是启动仍然出现了错误：</p>

<pre>
<code>rails uninitialized class variable @@schemes in URI (NameError) Did you mean?&nbsp; scheme_list</code></pre>

<p><code>根据提示，打开文件，</code></p>

<p><code>查看，</code>显然，URI中的类变量@@ class没有初始化。</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p><code>增加</code></p>

<pre>
<code>require &#39;uri&#39;

URI.class_variable_set(:@@schemes, {})</code></pre>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
